{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/why-taste-metal","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"92df0a70-b246-5394-b58c-ffe060466142","frontmatter":{"title":"为什么吃东西会有金属味道","hero":{"id":"9051a49c-3679-5ead-95b7-f15ba21a1edf","childImageSharp":{"id":"e65ca3e8-a353-5bf7-8171-c961c5dd4f55","fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5037593984962405,"src":"/static/fda16e82ad82f068bd6f85c573031747/14b42/scary-cat.jpg","srcSet":"/static/fda16e82ad82f068bd6f85c573031747/f836f/scary-cat.jpg 200w,\n/static/fda16e82ad82f068bd6f85c573031747/2244e/scary-cat.jpg 400w,\n/static/fda16e82ad82f068bd6f85c573031747/14b42/scary-cat.jpg 800w,\n/static/fda16e82ad82f068bd6f85c573031747/47498/scary-cat.jpg 1200w,\n/static/fda16e82ad82f068bd6f85c573031747/0e329/scary-cat.jpg 1600w,\n/static/fda16e82ad82f068bd6f85c573031747/947df/scary-cat.jpg 5472w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}},"date":"2019-10-18","path":"post/why-taste-metal","tags":["生活"]},"html":"<p>有段时间我吃饭总是有点儿金属味。我自己在家做饭，油、菜、调味料都不是劣质的，但觉得味道比外卖还要奇怪。我在网上查了一下，大部分搜索结果都是说可能是肠胃有问题，更严重的可能是肾脏问题，好吓人的……</p>\n<p>不过后来我终于发现了原因！我炒菜的生活有时候会接点儿水放在锅里以免糊了，或者是会放点儿水煮一煮。而且因为我贪方便，直接接自来水龙头中的水。后来我换用了纯净水来炒菜和蒸米饭，于是就没有金属味了！</p>\n<p>所以啊，很多状况未必是身体出了问题，千万不要「心急乱投医」，可能只是「生活方式」的问题。</p>\n<p><span class=\"uk-text-muted\">Photo by Volodymyr Hryshchenko on Unsplash</span></p>"},"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"CY Is Here"}}},"pageContext":{"pathName":"post/why-taste-metal","prev":{"frontmatter":{"path":"post/use-ffmpeg-to-extract-subtitles-from-videos","tags":["字幕","工具"],"title":"使用ffmpeg提取视频中的字幕"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"post/after-deploying-to-github-page-nuxtjs-site-cannot-show-images","tags":["Coding","Nuxt.js"],"title":"After Deploying to GitHub Page Nuxt.js Site Cannot Show Images"}}}}}